high_descs: Turn right, walk three steps, turn left, walk six steps, turn left, take one step to the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter sitting to the right of the lettuce.
Turn right to face the stove, cater-cornered.
Put the knife into the pan at the back of the stove, sitting vertical at the bottom, right corner of the pan.
Pick up the pan on the stove by the handle,
Turn right, take one step, turn right again taking three steps, turn left, take one step and stop at the table.
Put the pan in the center of the table directly in front of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the stove then turn left.
Pick up the butter knife that's in front of you.
Turn to your right.
Put the knife in the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan on the back right burner.
Turn right and take a step then turn right and take two steps then turn left and take a step.
Put the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Head to the counter that's to the left of the oven
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn to the right and face the oven
Put the knife in the container in the top right stove
Grab the container off of the top right stove
Turn around and go to the kitchen island
Put the container on the kitchen island
anns.task_desc: Putting a container with a knife in it on the kitchen island
